content:
If an agent's role changes or they switch teams, a supervisor can reassign them to a different queue. How you reassign an agent depends on your telephony provider:

*   Amazon Connect supports adding groups (routing profiles) to a queue.
*   Select the agents or groups to add to the queue from the dropdown in the Manage Queues dialog box.
*   Click Done.

This feature is available with Service Cloud Voice and Partner Telephony.
title: Reassigning Voice Queue Agents
